      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know it's a depressant but i'm not talking about getting drunk lol. just like, a small glass of wine to help me wind down. won't it just make the diazepam feel more effective? i just really need to sleep tonight and i feel like the tea isn't gonna do much.",
