    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i've heard from people that a tiny bit of alcohol actually helps sedatives work better for people with insomnia. like it just helps you hit that sleep state faster. if i only have like 4 or 5 ounces, is it really going to be a big deal? i feel like i can manage it and i just really can't afford to be up all night again.",
